⇦ 2014 2016 ⇨

Top 3 Artists Who Released their Debut Recording in 2015

These artists released their first recording in 2015, which makes them eligible for the Rock & Roll Hall of Fame in 2040. All currently eligible artists are listed here. Artists aleady inducted in the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame can be found here.

1. Dua Lipa2. Camila Cabello3. Post Malone

Missing someone? They may be listed in a different year. Check this list before letting us know.
